{"tid":410561,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人既屋企人成世都接受唔到貓狗？","createTime":"2017-09-23T04:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T11:39:00.000Z","uid":102763,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a5093b36dedcf7cbb5f5d46e634f076cb0cea69","tid":410561,"uid":102763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"小弟之前養隻貓。比屋企人日日話我。<br />\n頭果三四個月佢地見左隻貓又話扔左佢。又成咁<br />\n之前隻貓做錯小小野又比佢又打又話要扔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家過左成年。有一日隻貓有小小唔舒服。<br />\n佢地工都唔番。請假車隻貓去睇病。睇成千蚊。<br />\n到我唔舒服到冇力行路。老母一句叫左你早d訓嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n依家仲日日霸住隻貓自己玩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇。時間可以令佢地改觀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有。貓狗相處再耐都冇用"},{"pid":"e9b2a9d5e2655cea06ddaa4a7db16d6b9d8d6917","tid":410561,"uid":92600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:59:09.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n到而家都唔肯掂隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7fbfb99f168148d6c2a0b1a58e490c11382dd2","tid":410561,"uid":102763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<br />\n到而家都唔肯掂隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解。係唔係佢對貓過敏炸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c719a0244f50112f53abacfe39c9731700e3cbe","tid":410561,"uid":92600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有<br />\n到而家都唔肯掂隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解。係唔係佢對貓過敏炸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為真係唔鍾意小動物"},{"pid":"87c5230e62d73e365b4d6b181d462dfe2467fa1f","tid":410561,"uid":78392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:38:07.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e3e12ce02475ceb4c1505b7cd03fbfb1dbb254","tid":410561,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:39:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有<br />\n到而家都唔肯掂隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解。係唔係佢對貓過敏炸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為真係唔鍾意小動物</blockquote><br />\n過左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}